Invocation Name: k. fox digital radio
des: KFOX Digital Radio is an engaging music mix station that brings together a rich variety of genres in one place. Our extensive playlist features Jazz, R&B, Pop, Country, Alternative, Soft Rock, Zydeco, Blues, Oldies, and Gospel, ensuring a diverse and enjoyable listening experience for all. We are dedicated to Keeping the whole Family feeling Optimistic and Xhilarated with our carefully curated selection of music. Whether you're in the mood for the soulful rhythms of R&B, the nostalgic charm of Oldies, or the lively beats of Zydeco, KFOX Digital Radio provides the perfect sound to elevate your mood and brighten your day. Our goal is to create a positive, energized and sometimes mellowed atmosphere where every member of the family can find joy and inspiration.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
